{"tid":1680903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［震驚14億人］原來林鄭係反社會人格？！","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T13:55:44.000Z","uid":299383,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"97c35fb1e6c42b9a0269e50f40bb2b2299b5695d","tid":1680903,"uid":299383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"見到今日單新聞「女G4暈低 特首轉身而去」，難免想問點解有人涼薄冷血成咁？就算condom跌落地下，你都會執返掉落垃圾桶啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋佢之前 笑住頒獎畀消防遺孀、天皇典禮玩電話、畀人影到喪禮笑住走+消費死者etc<br />\n唔係因為佢做人冇公關，而係生性如此！唔會理其他人感受。<br />\n<br />\n而佢一直我行我素，唔輸得，覺得自己啱嗮，錯永遠係市民，民望低只會覺得自己委屈。<br />\n唔係因為佢好打得、唔係因為考開第一。而係佢根本冇自省能力！只會怪罪於人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n種種跡象表明......真相只有一個！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uayxLoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuayxLoq.jpg&h=72b35aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: Kumar and Clark&rsquo;s 9E p930<br />\n<br />\n佢係「反社會人格障礙者」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n低智商型反社會人格障礙，係會傾向暴力同犯罪。<br />\n但若然係高智商者，就會表現到「好打得」，職場扶搖直上，位高權重。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得一直睇唔透佢諗乜&mdash;&mdash;可以行每步棋都錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畀個反社會人格障礙者做到特首，想唔攬炒都難。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab06e28a29972bd92b6cb8e6e51c2c57c0b0e7c","tid":1680903,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12179d2ee90bac20fb4bd365b0db01714681878e","tid":1680903,"uid":3439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"唔出奇"},{"pid":"9607b40eafac02c89cf3da21e4fff383d3eaa3d8","tid":1680903,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"eddc40dffb1fd5ef24ad4c0b0f57b9b101f1254a","tid":1680903,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:50:54.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=e82cc69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"8d4d108b2d2232f5b24a32da7e77d3f7a7370214","tid":1680903,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"教大家一招KO林鄭成個取消區議會計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db2f066da84b